# demos/web-search.tape — Web search with SearXNG
Output demos/web-search.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "hello"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "what happened at KubeCon this week?"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Type "summarize the top 3 announcements"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "exit"
Enter
